The paper discusses energy efficiency in the context of 5G networks, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer networks and communications (cs.NI). The paper also discusses power consumption models and optimization techniques, which are topics that fall under information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses hybrid MM systems, which involve the use of multiple technologies and therefore could fall under the categories of augmented reality (cs.AR) and systems and control (cs.SY).
